org.fax4j.bridge.email

Class DefaultMailMessageParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fax4j.bridge.AbstractRequestParser<javax.mail.Message>
      • org.fax4j.bridge.email.DefaultMailMessageParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MailMessageParser, RequestParser<javax.mail.Message>, Initializable

    public class DefaultMailMessageParser
extends AbstractRequestParser<javax.mail.Message>
implements MailMessageParser
    This class provides default predefined implementation of the HTTP request parser used to extract the fax job and file info from the HTTP request.
    This default parser expects the mail message as follows:
    • Subject line: fax:[number] where number is the target address
    • From email address would be used as sender email
    • First attachment (or in case of none, the body text) would be used as the fax data
    Since:
    0.41.3
    Version:
    1.01
    Author:
    Sagie Gur-Ari
